### Problem Found: 6v2 Regression
- losing_territory fires at step 500 when enemy has 3+ more junctions
- In 6v2, opponent's 2 agents focus on junctions while our 6 disperse = early junction deficit
- Scramblers activate prematurely, reducing aligner count when we should overwhelm
- **Fix (v918/v919)**: Only trigger scrambler shift for majority teams on severe loss (enemy > friendly*2 + 5)

